title: First MC DAO multisig purchase
body:
Through the passed proposals on snapshot for purchasing, we have:

2 Floor CryptoPunks
10 Floor BAYC
Land in Sandbox

This vote will include 2 Floor CryptoPunks and 10 Floor BAYC, since Sandbox land needs to be discussed thoroughly and have its own personal vote, which would be quite complex and not make sense to be put in this list. However, It will be an option in the future when the land is proposed on snapshot and agreed upon. The two options CryptoPunks and BAYC, will have one winner on this round, and if either one loses, they will be included in the next snapshot vote. 

Floor = Sweep minimum floor.

Please vote accordingly.
